            <entry xml:id="entry_ælǧīn" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                <form xml:id="form_d2609e66" type="lemma"><orth>ælǧīn</orth></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense xml:id="sense_d2609e72"><sense xml:id="sense_d2609e73"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>скупой</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>stingy</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d2609e82"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>алчный</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>greedy</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp xml:id="exampleGrp_d2609e92">
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2609e94">
                        <quote>aftæ ælǧīn ū, æmæ jæ mystytæ dær fælyǧdysty</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>он так скуп, что даже мыши от него разбежались</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>he is so stingy that even the mice fled from him</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>III
                            190</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, тот же корень, что в <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ælǧ"/> 'отвращение’ (%iælǧīn%i ‘внушающий отвращение’); ср.
                        <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e170" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e118" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>argānd, arǧanda</w>
                        <gloss><q>алчный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e178" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e126" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>жадный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e184" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e132" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>возбужденный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e190" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e138" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>гневный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e197" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e145" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arɣant (ʼrɣʼnt)</w>
                        <gloss><q>алчный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e205" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e153" xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>гнусный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e211" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e159" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>әrәɣant-</w></mentioned>. Конечное %i-in%i может восходить к
                    %i-aina-%i.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, the same root as in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ælǧ"/> 'disgust’ (%iælǧīn%i ‘disgusting'); cf. <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e118" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e170" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>argānd, arǧanda</w>
                        <gloss><q>avid</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e126" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e178" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>greedy</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e132" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e184" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>excited</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e138" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e190" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>angry</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e145" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e197" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arɣant (ʼrɣʼnt)</w>
                        <gloss><q>avid</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e153" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e205" xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>vile</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2609e159" xml:id="mentioned_d2609e211" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>әrәɣant-</w></mentioned>. The final %i-in%i may go back to
                    %i-aina-%i.</etym>
